      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i live in oslo and since its winter and basically dark all the time i've been feeling pretty low energy. i read online that taking a huge amount of vitamin d can fix that and boost the immune system way faster. is it actually safe if I take like 50,000 iu every day for a few weeks to just get my levels up quickly?",
