      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but the 1000 iu thing feels so low when i'm feeling this bad. some wellness influencers say that \"loading doses\" are actually standard for people who are severely deficient to jumpstart the system. if i only do it for like 2 or 3 weeks, wouldn't my body just use it up before it becomes toxic? it seems like a quick fix for the winter slump.",
